|archive-date=2015-09-24 
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924143325/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20130726/231283/ 
|dead-url=no 
}}</ref>。其中演出[[王小棣|王小棣]]導演作品《[[刺蝟男孩|刺蝟男孩]]》及《剪刀‧石頭‧布》<ref>{{cite web 
|url=http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/entertainment/paper/766057 
